Package edu.cs.uga.DatabaseTermProject.model

Class Category

java.lang.Object
edu.cs.uga.DatabaseTermProject.model.Category
public class Category
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents a category. Each category contains a string name and a id. The category has a minimum, maximum, average, and review score. It also contains the amount of products sold.
